<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>crazy as a loon • crazy like a fox</xh5><p> <i>crazy as a loon</i>—(coll.) very silly; insane: If you think you can get away with that, you’re as <u>crazy as a loon</u>.</p><p> <i>crazy like a fox</i>—(coll.) very sly, cunning, or shrewd: Don’t let him fool you. He’s <u>crazy like a fox</u>.</p> </entry>
